# Implementation Plan - Yakuzen "Fuuka" Website

## Goal
Create a high-quality, professional single-page website for a Yakuzen (Medicinal Cooking) restaurant called "Fuuka". The design should reflect a Japanese aesthetic, be responsive, and have a catchy First View to drive reservations.

## User Review Required
- **Design Direction:** "Japanese Professional Designer" style.
- **Key Elements:** Vertical text usage, Noto Serif JP font, generous whitespace.

